@baseUrl = http://localhost:3333
@appointmentId = 1
@accessToken = COLE_SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### [SUCESSO] Atualizar status para completed
# Esperado: 200 com status completed
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed"
}

###

### [SUCESSO] Atualizar status para canceled
# Esperado: 200 com status canceled
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "canceled"
}

###

### [SUCESSO] Atualizar status para no_show
# Esperado: 200 com status no_show
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "no_show"
}

###

### [FALHA] Agendamento inexistente
# Esperado: 404 NotFoundError
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/999999/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed"
}

###

### [FALHA] Tentativa de alterar agendamento já finalizado
# Esperado: 409 ConflictError
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed"
}

###

### [FALHA] Status inválido
# Esperado: 422 Validation Error com campo status nos issues
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "scheduled"
}

###

### [FALHA] ID inválido no path
# Esperado: 422 Validation Error
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/abc/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed"
}

###

### [FALHA] Sem token de autenticação
# Esperado: 401 UnauthorizedError
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed"
}

###

### [FALHA] Token de outro prestador (sem permissão para atualizar este agendamento)
# Pré-requisito: @accessToken pertence ao prestador id=2; agendamento id=1 pertence ao id=1
# Esperado: 403 ForbiddenError
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed"
}